displayProperties.name: Kalli, the Corrupted
displayProperties.description: Kalli, an Awoken Techeun who serves Queen Mara Sov, was Taken by Oryx and transformed into Kalli, the Corrupted. Free her.

displayProperties.name: Shuro Chi, the Corrupted
displayProperties.description: Shuro Chi, an Awoken Techeun who serves Queen Mara Sov, was Taken by Oryx and transformed into Shuro Chi, the Corrupted. Free her.

displayProperties.name: Morgeth, the Spirekeeper
displayProperties.description: Morgeth, the Spirekeeper, an enormous and powerful Taken Ogre, serves as the enforcer of Riven's corruption in the Dreaming City, and the guard of the City's main tower, The Keep of Voices. Destroy them.

displayProperties.name: The Vault
displayProperties.description: A locking mechanism which secures the immensely powerful and treacherous.

displayProperties.name: Riven of a Thousand Voices
displayProperties.description: Riven, the last known Ahamkara, formerly in the service of Mara Sov, was Taken by Oryx. She now corrupts the city from its heart at the behest of the Hive queen, Savathûn.

displayProperties.name: Crypt Security
displayProperties.description: Penetrate the Bray facility's security protocols and gain access to the Deep Stone Crypt.

displayProperties.name: Atraks-1
displayProperties.description: Counter the self-duplicating, Exo-reborn, Atraks-1.

displayProperties.name: Taniks, Reborn
displayProperties.description: Interrupt the station's Nuclear Descent Protocol and secure it from Taniks.

displayProperties.name: Taniks, the Abomination
displayProperties.description: Thwarting Taniks made him grow stronger. Destroy him, once and for all...

displayProperties.name: Confluxes
displayProperties.description: Secure Vex constructs by preventing Vex sacrifices.

displayProperties.name: Oracles
displayProperties.description: Counter the Oracles' song or be marked for negation and lost to time.

displayProperties.name: The Templar
displayProperties.description: An extremely powerful Vex Hydra, The Templar is unique in it being a creature out of time. As such, it can manipulate reality in accordance to the Oracles' design.

displayProperties.name: The Gatekeepers
displayProperties.description: Protectors of the Glass Throne, the Gatekeepers are Vex Hydras who stand as the Throne's last defence.

displayProperties.name: Atheon, Time's Conflux
displayProperties.description: The Axis Mind responsible for bridging the Vex's own calculations into existence.

displayProperties.name: Acquisition
displayProperties.description: Fulfil the requirements and pierce the veil.

displayProperties.name: Collection
displayProperties.description: Subdue and destroy the abomination.

displayProperties.name: Exhibition
displayProperties.description: Reorient your perspective.

displayProperties.name: Dominion
displayProperties.description: Meet the destroyer, Rhulk.

displayProperties.name: Evade the Consecrated Mind
displayProperties.description: Evade Voltaic Overload charges and pursue the Consecrated Mind.

displayProperties.name: Summon the Consecrated Mind
displayProperties.description: Bypass Vex confluxes and force out the Consecrated Mind from hiding.

displayProperties.name: Defeat the Consecrated Mind
displayProperties.description: Once and for all, defeat the Consecrated Mind.

displayProperties.name: The Sanctified Mind
displayProperties.description: A Vex Axis Mind, the Sanctified Mind amasses control over many Vex. Defeat it to prevent further incursions by the Sol Divisive outside of the Black Garden.

displayProperties.name: Basilica
displayProperties.description: Influence hive ritual magic by controlling annihilator totems.

displayProperties.name: Warpriest
displayProperties.description: Defeat Oryx's Warpriest before he destroys you.

displayProperties.name: Golgoroth
displayProperties.description: Subdue the abomination.

displayProperties.name: The Daughters
displayProperties.description: Interrupt the the sisters' concentration.

displayProperties.name: Oryx
displayProperties.description: Dethrone the king.

displayProperties.name: Cataclysm
displayProperties.description: Beat back Shadow Legion forces and pursue Nezarec.

displayProperties.name: Scission
displayProperties.description: Enter the Root.

displayProperties.name: Macrocosm
displayProperties.description: Align worlds and defeat the Explicator.

displayProperties.name: Nezarec
displayProperties.description: End the nightmare and defeat Nezarec.

displayProperties.name: Abyss
displayProperties.description: Follow the light.

displayProperties.name: Bridge
displayProperties.description: Traverse the bridge and climb the Throne.

displayProperties.name: Ir Yût, the Deathsinger
displayProperties.description: Strike down the witch, silence their Deathsong.

displayProperties.name: Crota, Son of Oryx
displayProperties.description: Defeat the Son of Oryx.
